txt.en: 'Where is it that you come from?'
Register your heritage with the notary.

'Ah... Lórien.\n\n'You come from Lothlórien, the fabled golden woods whose Elves dwell high in the mallorn-trees and are ruled by Celeborn, wisest of the Eldar of Middle-earth, and the Lady Galadriel.'
